					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介", "Junnosuke"},
					"“Which is why there’s nothing more arousing to a person than having a girl show you her underwear while looking at you with disdain.”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介"},
					"“所以被人露出讨厌的表情一面给看内裤的行为，会产生无上的兴奋──”",
